   Building 1, Wilson Hall

   12:00 Noon
     __________________________________________________________________

   Friday, October 12, 2001
   Beverly A. Mock, Ph.D., Laboratory of Genetics, NCI
   "Efficiency alleles as Genetic Modifiers of Susceptibility to
   Plasmacytomagenesis"

   Friday, October 26, 2001
   Kevin E. Brown, M.D., Hematology Branch, NHLBI
   "An animal model of parvovirus B19 Infection"

